results.title: LOVE BIRDS Tea Light Card (for battery tea lights)
results.description:
This is a LOVE BIRDS version of a new Tea Light card! This card looks like a regular card in the front, with a graphic of a sweet bird with glittery pink swirls. The base card stock is a beautiful print all about love. When you open the card, a box lantern appears in the center of a turquoise foil leaf card stock background. On the left panel of the lantern is one view of birds in a bird cage, and on the right panel of the lantern is a different view of birds in a bird cage. Both panels are on white vellum. Turn the card to the back, and there is a blank piece of white card stock on which to write a personal message. Envelope included.

Tea Light cards are made to stand up when opened. I just started making these, and love the unexpected nature of them! It is a great way to display special art, both during the day, and also at night. The vellum makes it so that the lantern will glow softly when it is placed over a battery-operated tea light. Envelope included. (Note: Battery-operated tea light is NOT included.)

Warning! 
NOT TO BE USED WITH CANDLES!   
USE ONLY WITH BATTERY-OPERATED LED TEA LIGHTS!
